How to Request Account Deletion
If you wish to delete your account and associated data, please follow these steps:

1. Log in to your account using the mobile app or website.
2. Navigate to Settings and select Account Management.
3. Click on Request Account Deletion and follow the on-screen instructions.
4. You may be required to verify your identity via email or phone number.
5. Once confirmed, your request will be processed, and you will receive a confirmation email.

If you experience any issues, you can contact our support team through the app‚Äôs help section or at [support@primestage.in].

What Happens When You Delete Your Account?
When you delete your account, the following data will be permanently removed from our servers:

‚úÖ Deleted Data:

1. Personal profile details (name, email, phone number).
2. Booking history and past transactions.
3. Uploaded media (photos, videos, or documents).
4. Any other user-generated content.

üö´ Data That May Be Retained:

